decks.notes: This Orzhov Midrange deck focuses on aggressive plays and utilizing sacrifice mechanics to generate card advantage and control the board. By combining cards like Village Rites, Chthonian Nightmare, Marionette Apprentice, and Gravecrawler, the deck can quickly overwhelm opponents and drain their life total. The inclusion of Thoughtseize helps disrupt opponents' game plans, while cards like Unearth and Warren Soultrader provide recursion and flexibility. The mana base is designed to support the deck's aggressive game plan while still enabling consistent casting of its spells.
